---
title: English Lamb Roast & Peppercorn Sauce with Rosemary Potatoes & Cheesy Baked Cauliflower
description: A roast lamb is a signature when it comes to a classic English roast dinner. We’ve paired ours with a delightful peppercorn sauce,
which will soak into the tender meat as it's served. With oven-roasted spuds and a creamy cauliflower bake, sitting down to enjoy
this dish will be the most satisfying part of your day - we guarantee it!
